com.iha.emulator.server

Class DatabaseInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iha.emulator.server.DatabaseInfo

  • public class DatabaseInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class holding information needed for connection to database. All information are set by EmulatorServer from configuration file, except database name, which is included in every message from client.
    Author:
    Filip Sutovsky
